body:
```
/Pytorch/pytorch/test/common.py:211: RuntimeWarning: overflow encountered in ubyte_scalars
```
is not printed by PyTorch, but by NumPy. This is likely the reason why you're seeing this. Add `print(asarray[i], wrapped_x[i])` before [this line](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/test/test_torch.py?utf8=✓#L4349) and make sure the outputs match
